OL,5, Three gambling firms owned by William  
OL,6, Hill are to pay penalties of #19.2m for
OL,7, failing to protect consumers and weak  
OL,8, anti-money laundering controls.        
OL,10,FThe record penalty comes after the     
OL,11,FGambling Commission found "widespread  
OL,12,Fand alarming" issues at the company.   
OL,14,FThe problems were so severe the        
OL,15,Fcommission had "seriously considered"  
OL,16,Fsuspending the firm's licence.         
OL,18,FIn one case, a customer was allowed to 
OL,19,Fopen a new account and spend #23,000 in
OL,20,F20 minutes without any checks.         
